	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi binas tuas literas, compater charissime; eas, quas inscripseras d. d. <persName>Gessnero</persName>, curavi ipsi protinus tradi.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod scribam, nunc non habeo, nisi quod illi, qui ex <placeName type="auto_name">Gallia</placeName> veniunt, pro certo referunt persequtionem opera et instinctu <placeName type="auto_name">Guysianorum</placeName> et rasorum unctorumque maledicto chrismate, chara[c]tere bestiae, progredi.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus, qui regem potenter cohercuit, potest et infelix illud avicium per acsipitrem aliquem dispellere et in fugam convertere.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc totus occupatus sum scribendis literis et mittendis <placeName>Francfordiam</placeName>, ut inde in varias nationes ad amicos perferantur.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mitto tibi et d. <persName type="auto_name">Gallicio Sermones</persName> nostros in Ieremiam nunc aeditos.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Puto me tibi et <persName type="auto_name">Gallicio</persName> nostram catechesim misisse; si non misi, submittam adhuc.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Benigne haec a me accipite.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wenn ich üch anders gern schanckte, hätte ichs nitt; acht ouch, das sye ein komliche und üch fuͦgeliche schäncke.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Valete.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta d. d. consules, <persName type="auto_name">Philippum</persName> etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Com[m]end me legato et saluta illum amicissime; scribam ad eum, si aliquid memoratu dignum ex nundinis accepero.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri 25. augusti anno 1559.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bullingerus tuissimus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Darunter von <persName type="auto_name">Fabricius Hand</persName> die Notiz:]</note>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">20. augusti <persName>Ferdinandus</persName> post soluta comitia <placeName>Augusta</placeName> discessit <placeName>Viennam</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
